Short: Value the insight result used as input
Definition: Value the insight result used as input; This element is to be used when the value leveraged as input to the insight is not an extracted span of text. Note this is different than the value the insight is about. It is instead a value from another element or reference that was used in evaluating the insight. For example, if the insight pertains to a zip code value, the based-on-value may be a city name that has been specified in another element.
